data.description: Step into the light-filled interior designed to captivate from the moment you step through the door of 217 Timber Grove Ct. Upon entry, you'll be greeted with sightlines through the main living spaces, decorative archways & art niches + ceramic wood-like tile throughout the entire first floor. To your right is a dedicated Office w/ double French door for privacy. The vaulted ceilings & wall of windows in the open concept living spaces is inviting & perfect for entertaining family and friends. Enjoy evenings by the fire with the floor-to-ceiling stone gas log fireplace with a wooden mantle perfect for Holidays. Cherish your private & spacious primary retreat complete with double closets and sinks + a separate shower & soaking tub for relaxation. Upstairs, you'll find a Game Room loft area, an oversized Media Room wired for surround sound + 3 great sized bedrooms and the additional full bathroom. Located at the end of a Cul-de-Sac, this property is truly a gem with room for all!
